Bug.WithStack:
I20030604:

	public TestResult run() {
		TestResult result= createResult();
		run(result);
		TestResult result1= createResult();
		run(result1);
	}

Qyuickfix proposes to return result1. It should also propose to return result.
fixed in 3.0 M2

